summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Fifty-ninth Street from 24th Avenue N.W. to 32nd Avenue N. W. et al, in the City of Seattle., by constructing watermains under Ordinance No. 23890 creating Local Improvement District No. 2308 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
